      "title": "3,740 metric tonnes of gas is arriving today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The ship loaded with 3700 metric tonnes of gas arrived in the country yesterday (10).",
        "A second vessel carrying 3,740 metric tonnes of gas will also arrive today.",
        "Also, the Presidential Media Division has mentioned that the third ship loaded with 3,200 metric tons of gas will arrive in the country on the 15th.",
        "In this case, the President's Media Division has announced that gas distribution will be regular and regular from July 12.",
        "By the end of this month, the problem related to gas demand for homes will be completely resolved, Litro CEO Mudittha Peiris said. (a)"
